    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable Lock differential. Technical highlights include a recently overhauled double-VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension retains its signature precision with updated bushings and Bilstein monotube dampers. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals are dialed in, including a recent valve adjustment and cooling system refresh. It is a tactile, analog machine optimized for performance and longitudinal grip.",
